Package: aic8800dc-tenda-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms, build-essential, kmod, eject, usb-modeswitch
Recommends: linux-headers-generic | linux-headers-amd64 | linux-headers
Description: DKMS driver for Tenda AX300 W311MI AIC8800DC adapters
 Out-of-tree AIC8800DC Wi-Fi driver with Tenda USB IDs 2604:0013 and
 2604:0014 enabled. The package includes firmware, a USB mass-storage
 mode-switch rule, module auto-loading, and DKMS integration for kernel
 upgrades.
